name: Leonardo Da Vinci
skill: Deals 4853/5793 DMG to the enemy with the highest ATK, with a very high chance of inflicting Paralysis.
ability: Sharply increases DMG dealt and slightly reduces DMG taken.

additional_data.description: The spirit of the Renaissance Period's most famous and multi-talented artist. Everyone calls him a genius, and he has to admit they're right. They say he was even involved with the founding of the Bureau. More recently he's been getting into doll-making. He even made a doll for the Bureau, but it didn't work out too well and he ended up getting kicked off the Support Item Development Team. That's why he started getting sent off on random assignments. But in the meantime he continues to gather parts and try to improve his creation.
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Summon rate increased until 08/2/17
◦ Initially, his sprite's hair color was a dirty blonde.

skill: "You just have to hit them in the right spot!"
